resources.string: Ifoni yakho ingakuthumela izexwayiso, njengemiyalelo yokuphuma, phakathi nenhlekelele yemvelo. Le sevisi iyinhlanganyelo ephakathi Kwesikhungo Sokuphathwa Kwezimo Eziphuthumayo Sikazwelonke, abahlinzeki benethiwekhi, kanye nabakhiqizi bedivayisi.\10\10Ungahle ungazitholi izexwayiso uma kunenkinga ngedivayisi yakho noma uma izimo zenethiwekhi zingezinhle.
